<div class="container" style="max-width:1400px">
  <h1 class="mt-5 mb-5 pt-5 text-center">Meet the Team</h1>
  <div class="profile-container w-100 d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-between">
    <div class="profile d-flex flex-column align-items-center" style="width:275px">
      <%= image_tag "Piotr.jpg", class: "rounded-circle shadow",
                                style: "width: 275px; height: 275px; object-fit:cover;",
                                atl: "Photo of LoopyEx team member Piotr" %>
      <h2 class="mt-3"><a href="https://github.com/PiotrekCodes">Piotr</a></h2>
      <p class="fs-5 text-justify">Piotr is our UK-based master coder.
      When he's not making sure LoopyEx is running properly, he's shot putting his 👶🏼👶🏼 out of the Zoom screen
      view. He knitted this jumper at the wee age of 3!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="profile d-flex flex-column align-items-center" style="width:275px">
      <%= image_tag "Dari.jpg", class: "rounded-circle shadow",
                                style: "width: 275px; height: 275px; object-fit:cover;",
                                atl: "Photo of LoopyEx team member Dari" %>
      <h2 class="mt-3"><a href="https://github.com/DariBerrie">Dari</a></h2>
      <p class="fs-5 text-justify">Back-end extraordinaire, Dari will (hopefully) solve all of your database issues.
      She's the knitter behind LoopyEx's creation and will take things one stitch 🧶 and one line of code at a time!
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="profile d-flex flex-column align-items-center" style="width:275px">
      <%= image_tag "Zsuzsanna.jpg", class: "rounded-circle shadow",
                                style: "width: 275px; height: 275px; object-fit:cover;",
                                atl: "Photo of LoopyEx team member Zsuzsanna" %>
      <h2 class="mt-3"><a href="https://github.com/zynolia">Zsuzsanna</a></h2>
      <p class="fs-5 text-justify">Like Co-Pilot 👩🏻‍✈️ on our VS Code (joke!), Zsuzsanna will always be there to guide and keep
       us on the right path. She codes and knits with a hawk's eye and attention to detail that are unmatched!
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="profile d-flex flex-column align-items-center" style="width:275px">
      <%= image_tag "Amanda.jpg", class: "rounded-circle shadow",
                                style: "width: 275px; height: 275px; object-fit:cover;",
                                atl: "Photo of LoopyEx team member Amanda" %>
      <h2 class="mt-3"><a href="https://github.com/AmandaPerino">Amanda</a></h2>
      <p class="fs-5 text-justify">Amanda is the LoopyEx evangelist 🗽, spreading the good word in the fiber arts community.
      When she's not travelling to yarn conferences and giving interviews, she's also diving  into LoopyEx's software stack.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
